text: František Kříž (18 May 1884 - 30 July 1966) was a fencer who competed for Bohemia in 1912 and Czechoslovakia in 1928. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Czech male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Bohemia Category:Olympic fencers of Czechoslovakia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Fencers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague Category:Place of death missing
